org.apache.click.extras.cayenne
Class TabbedCayenneForm

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.click.control.AbstractControl
      org.apache.click.control.AbstractContainer
          org.apache.click.control.Form
              org.apache.click.extras.cayenne.CayenneForm
                  org.apache.click.extras.cayenne.TabbedCayenneForm
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Control, Container, Stateful
public class TabbedCayenneForm
extends CayenneForm

Provides Cayenne data aware tabbed Form control:   <form method='POST'>.

This control provides tab capabilities to the standard CayenneForm. For more information and examples please see:

  • CayenneForm
  • TabbedForm

CSS and JavaScript resources

In addition to Form's resources, the TabbedCayenneForm control makes use of the following resources (which Click automatically deploys to the application directory, /click):
  • click/extras-control.css
To import these TabbedCayenneForm files simply reference the variables $headElements and $jsElements in the page template.

render

public void render(HtmlStringBuffer buffer)
Render the HTML representation of the form.

The form will be rendered using the classpath template: 

 /org/apache/click/extras/control/TabbedForm.htm
If the form contains errors after processing, these errors will be rendered.
